<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #343a40;
            font-size: 28px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            color: #495057;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .otp {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #007bff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #007bff;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #868e96;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>OTP Verification</h1>
        <p>Hi <%= username %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering! Please verify your email address by entering the OTP below:</p>
        <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <a href="#" class="button">Verify Now</a>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
